# HSBC Loans Portal — Angular 13.3.11 to React 18 Migration Rules
# ================================================================
# Source repo: https://github.com/cogdeasy/red-angular-13.3.11
# Target: React 18.3.x + Vite + TypeScript 5.x

## Project Context

- name: hsbc-loans-portal
- source_framework: Angular 13.3.11
- target_framework: React 18.3.x (LTS)
- coexistence_strategy: single-spa
- styling: SCSS (HSBC Design System tokens migrated to CSS custom properties)
- state_management: Zustand (shared/global), TanStack Query (server state)
- forms: React Hook Form + Zod
- routing: React Router 6
- testing: Vitest + React Testing Library + Playwright
- bundler: Vite 5.x
- node_version: ">=18.0.0"

## Architecture Rules

